齿苋、鲜雷公根、鲜番木瓜等。第四为胃经，占10.06%，如鲜葱白、鲜忍冬藤、鲜白茅根、鲜苦楝皮等。鲜动物药主要入肝、脾、肾经。详见表3。</p><table-wrap id="table3" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table3">Table 3</xref></label><caption><title> Distribution rules of fresh herbs in meridian</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >归经</th><th align="center" valign="middle" ></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >鲜植物药</th><th align="center" valign="middle" ></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >鲜动物药</th><th align="center" valign="middle" ></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >合计</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >频数</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >频率</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >频数</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >频率</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >频数</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >频率</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >肝</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >84</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >25.07</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >7</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >53.85</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >91</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >26.15</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >心</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >25</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >7.46</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >7.69</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >26</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >7.47</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >脾</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >46</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >13.73</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >15.38</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >48</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >13.79</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >肺</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >66</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >19.70</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0</td><td align="cent